{
  "text": "Wnt-signaling modulators dharma Suppresses wnt8 expression in the organizer precursor cells. [CITATION_1] dkk1b Extracellular Wnt-antagonist, which binds to Lrp6. [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] foxa3 Inhibits dorsal activation of wnt8 transcription. [CITATION_5] mst1 Tumor suppressor; homologue of Drosophila hippo. [CITATION_6] [CITATION_7] foxd3 Suppresses dkk1 activation in the mesendoderm. [CITATION_8] fzd8b A putative receptor of Wnt-signaling.",
